---
import mango_tree from "../assets/mangotreesway.gif";
import ToolsSelector from "./ToolsSelector";
---

<section class="pb-16 px-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex items-center">
      <!-- <div class="w-1/2 pr-8"> -->
        <div class="w-1/2 pr-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-[#609949] text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
            Tools for a safer internet
          </div>
          <div class="text-gray-800 mb-6">
            CIB Mango Tree is a growing library of tools designed to detect
            signs of coordinated inauthentic behavior. It runs locally on your
            computer through an interactive command-line interface. Instead of
            scraping data, our programs analyze datasets of social media
            activity that you provide to identify abnormal online activity.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-1/2 flex justify-center items-center pl-8">
          <img
            src={mango_tree.src}
            alt="Mango tree illustration"
            class="max-w-full h-auto"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <ToolsSelector client:load />
    <!-- </div> -->
  </div>
</section>
